[4] Colombia: imported
Date: Fri 24 Jun 2022 4:06 PM GMT+2
Source: Reuters [abridged, edited]
https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/colombia-reports-first-cases-monkeypox-2022-06-24/


Colombia confirmed its 1st 3 cases of monkeypox in adults who had traveled from Europe and are now in quarantine, the country's health ministry said.

Of the 3 cases, 2 of the were found in the capital Bogota, and the 3rd was found in Colombia's 2nd city, Medellin.

[Reporting: Luis Jaime Acosta; writing: Oliver Griffin; editing: Jonathan Oatis]

